{"title":"咕咕咕","time_limit":2000,"memory_limit":128,"tags":["线段树","树状数组","数据结构"],"operation":{"submit":"https://syzoj.com/problem/567#submit_code","submissions":"https://syzoj.com/submissions?problem_id=567","statistics":"https://syzoj.com/problem/567/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://syzoj.com/problem/567/testdata","discussion":"https://syzoj.com/discussion/problem/567"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"~~出题人作业写不完了，只好咕掉题目背景了~~\r\n\r\n现在给你一个长度为 $n$ 的序列 $a_1, a_2, ···, a_n$ 你需要支持这两种操作\r\n\r\n- 第一种操作的格式是 $1$ $x$ $y$ 表示 在 $x$ 这个位置上加上 $y$\r\n\r\n- 第二种操作的格式是 $2$ $l$ $r$ $k$ 表示求出 $v$\r\n\r\n$$ v = \\sum_{i = l}^{r} {(a_i + k)} ^ 3$$"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行 $n$ $m$ : \r\n\r\n$n$ 表示序列长度， $m$ 表示操作次数\r\n\r\n第二行 $n$ 个数 为 $a_1, a_2, ···, a_n$\r\n\r\n接下来 $m$ 行 : \r\n\r\n每行都是两种操作中的一种"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"对于每个操作 $2$ 每行一个输出"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输入\r\n```cpp\r\n5 5\r\n3 2 1 3 1 \r\n2 1 5 0\r\n1 5 1\r\n2 2 4 0\r\n2 1 4 0\r\n2 4 5 -1\r\n```\r\n\r\n输出\r\n```cpp\r\n64\r\n36\r\n63\r\n9\r\n```\r\n"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"- $30\\%$ 的数据 $0$ $<=$ $n, m$ $<=$ $100$\r\n\r\n- $100\\%$ 的数据 $0$ $<$ $n, m$ $<$ $1,000, 000$\r\n\r\n最初 $|a_i|$ $<=$ $100$\r\n\r\n对于每操作 $1$ 保证 ：\r\n\r\n- $1$ $<=$ $x$ $<=$ $n$ \r\n- $|y|$ <= $200$\r\n\r\n对于每种操作 $2$ 保证 ：\r\n\r\n- $1$ $<=$ $l$ $<=$ $r$ $<=$ $n$\r\n- $k$ $<=$ $200$\r\n\r\n"}]}